					</li>

				</ul>
				<h3>4.4 Third Party Cookiess</h3>
				<ul class="policy_item">
					<li>
						<i class="i_shuffle"></i>
						From time-to-time, Megam.co engages third parties to track and analyze usage and volume statistical information from individuals who visit the Company’s Web site. Megam.co may also use other third-party cookies to track the performance of Company advertisements. The information provided to third parties does not include personal information, but this information may be re-associated with personal information after the Company receives it.

						Megam.co may also contract with third-party advertising networks that collect IP addresses and other Web Site Navigational Information on the Company’s Web site and emails and on third-party Web sites. Ad networks follow your online activities over time by collecting Web Site Navigational Information through automated means, including through the use of cookies. They use this information to provide advertisements about products and services tailored to your interests. You may see these advertisements on other Web sites. This process also helps us manage and track the effectiveness of our marketing efforts. To learn more about these and other advertising networks and their opt-out instructions, click here.
					</li>
				</ul>
